snippet.title: Daniel Roy
snippet.description:
I'm a professional sleight-of-hand magician who makes videos about magic! I specialize in the techniques used by professional card cheats and also studied neurobiology in college. As a result, I like to explore the interaction between sleight-of-hand and sleight-of-mind as it appears in magic. In simpler terms, I make videos about how magicians (and card cheats, hustlers, fraudulent psychics, etc.) are able to trick your brain into tricking you! :)
